    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "45 mins seems okay i guess but i'm kinda worried about the transfer at kings cross specifically. it feels like such a huge station and if the train is even a little bit late it'll be a mess. are there any specific things i should watch out for that might slow me down more than just walking?",
